  ('dietitian-moex-10654', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關電解質在體內之分佈的敘述，何者為非？ 細胞外液主要的陽離子是鈉，主要的陰離子是氯 細胞外液鈉對鉀的當量比例Na：K=16：1 細胞內主要的陽離子是鉀，主要的陰離子是磷酸根 細胞內鈉對鉀的當量比例Na：K=1：16', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "de86e5e3c8c3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "794bf55cd1a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "112", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-10655', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '青春期增加的脂肪組織所造成的肥胖，屬於何種類型？ 脂肪細胞體積肥大，數目減少型肥胖  脂肪細胞體積維持，數目增多型肥胖 脂肪細胞體積肥大，數目增多型肥胖  脂肪細胞體積肥大，數目維持型肥胖', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "de86e5e3c8c3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "794bf55cd1a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "112", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
